{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"Sudahkah sampai kepadamu berita tentang (hari Kiamat)?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:2","price":"Pada hari itu banyak wajah yang tertunduk hina,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:3","price":"(karena) bekerja keras lagi kepayahan,","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:4","price":"mereka memasuki api yang sangat panas (neraka),","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:5","price":"diberi minum dari sumber mata air yang sangat panas.","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:6","price":"Tidak ada makanan bagi mereka selain dari pohon yang berduri,","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:7","price":"yang tidak menggemukkan dan tidak menghilangkan lapar.","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:8","price":"Pada hari itu banyak (pula) wajah yang berseri-seri,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:9","price":"merasa senang karena usahanya (sendiri),","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:10","price":"(mereka) dalam surga yang tinggi,","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:11","price":"di sana (kamu) tidak mendengar perkataan yang tidak berguna.","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:12","price":"Di sana ada mata air yang mengalir.","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:13","price":"Di sana ada dipan-dipan yang ditinggikan,","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:14","price":"dan gelas-gelas yang tersedia (di dekatnya),","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:15","price":"dan bantal-bantal sandaran yang tersusun,","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:16","price":"dan permadani-permadani yang terhampar.","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:17","price":"Maka tidakkah mereka memperhatikan unta, bagaimana diciptakan?","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:18","price":"Dan langit, bagaimana ditinggikan?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:19","price":"Dan gunung-gunung bagaimana ditegakkan?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:20","price":"Dan bumi bagaimana dihamparkan?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:21","price":"Maka berilah peringatan, karena sesungguhnya engkau (Muhammad) hanyalah pemberi peringatan.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:22","price":"Engkau bukanlah orang yang berkuasa atas mereka,","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:23","price":"kecuali (jika ada) orang yang berpaling dan kafir,","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:24","price":"maka Allah akan mengazabnya dengan azab yang besar.","arabic":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5991,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"88:25","price":"Sungguh, kepada Kami lah mereka kembali,","arabi